# AI-Powered Phishing Email Analyzer (Blue Team)

Detects phishing indicators in `.eml` or pasted text with rule-based checks and optional AI (OpenAI) explanations.

## Setup (Windows)
```powershell
py -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -r requirements.txt
setx OPENAI_API_KEY "sk-...your-key..."
setx GPT_MODEL "gpt-5"
# Reopen PowerShell, then:
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
# === 0) Create folder structure ===
$P = "phishing-email-analyzer"
New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $P,samples -Force | Out-Null

# === 1) .gitignore ===
@'
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
.env
.DS_Store
reports/
